 
Cross-DB ETL Sync POC – Designed automated, database-agnostic synchronization across PostgreSQL servers, improving DR readiness and compliance.

DNS Failover & Fallback POC – Implemented automated failover in dual-DC setup, ensuring uptime and business continuity during outages.

DNS & Firewall Automation – Built proactive monitoring flows (nslookup + Teams/email alerts) and automated firewall object creation (218+ entries), reducing tickets and operational costs.

Resource & EMS Automation – Managed on-demand resource allocation, firewall config validation, and multiple EMS automation updates, driving efficiency and faster resolution.

Other POCs & Optimizations – VM creation from cloned disks and Playwright vs Selenium evaluation, supporting cost control and tool standardization.

